data.description: Gorgeous Griffin Oaks Subdivision home in Central Point, built in 2002 by Michael Suzi Homes. This 4 bedroom/2 full bath home is beautifully appointed and well maintained. Upgrade features include hardwood floors, custom cabinets, granite counters, central vacuum, instant hot water, dual shower heads, walk-in closets and skylight, vaulted ceilings and ceiling fans. This split floor plan has a Master Suite with private bath and extra large walk-in closet. All bedrooms have large closet space. Property is fully landscaped with a large patio, and has great curb appeal. Beautiful outside with mature landscaping, water features, hot tub and lap pool.
